data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 2-story home boasts 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a large gameroom. Step inside to discover a generously sized family room perfect for gatherings and relaxation. The spacious kitchen is a chef's delight, offering ample counter space, modern appliances, and a breakfast bar. Entertain guests in the elegant formal dining room, or head upstairs to the huge game room for some fun-filled activities. The large primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring a walk-in closet, 2 vanities, a deep soaking tub, and a separate shower for ultimate luxury. Outside, the spacious fenced backyard provides the perfect setting for outdoor enjoyment and privacy. With its desirable features and prime location, this home is sure to exceed your expectations. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make 4206 Thyme Circle your forever home!
